{
  "stem": "26728.8",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were told about what was going on in New York City, in London, in Paris, and all these big cities, the parties.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had some booze, and we sat around in our nice hotel room in Linz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were so damn depressed that we tried to party, but we couldn't party.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It just-- it didn't mean a damn thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If anything, expression-wise, it was, God damn it, I don't want it to be over yet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, we're not through with this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We need to finish this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "These are from guys that-- that didn't want to-- they didn't want it to stop like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They wanted it to stop when they were fighting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "After what they'd seen, they wanted revenge.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They wanted to avenge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If there's a motive, I don't know whether I'm saying this right, it was, we have to find a way to avenge these people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In my opinion-- and this is only my opinion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I never had an opportunity.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could have bombed Mauthausen, I could've bombed Dachau, and I could have-- or strafed them both, but it was-- we were not told not to, but we were told to-- that was not a priority.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wouldn't do any good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, first of all, we did know about them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, I didn't know that Mauthausen was where Mauthausen was until I went to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know where Dachau was until I went to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew there were camps, but we weren't looking for that kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The guys that discovered the camps weren't looking for the camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Two camps were liberated on purpose by a general officer saying that is our destination.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was, uh, Dachau and Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
